pico-ctl (0.2.1-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Fix upload MemoryError: write file chunks incrementally instead of
    concatenating all decoded data in RAM.
  * Add gc.collect() before and after file writes on the Pico.
  * Detect MemoryError during upload and show actionable error message.

